value: Indon, PNG, New Guinea, New Britain, New Guinea, New Ireland
Palearctic winter visitor, wetlands and coast: Sahel zone and south to L. Victoria, fewer to Zambia.
Shallow inland lakes, ponds, and streams bordered with dense emergent vegetation, reed beds or marshes; winters primarily on fresh-water but also in marine or brackish situations.
